data.description: Adorable Ranch, nestled in a desirable Bellingham Neighborhood, featuring a fire place in the living room, east in kitchen, with a great sun room that is so bright and sunny.  This home also features three bedrooms, one bath with laundry set up, on a quiet dead end side street with a nice size back yard for the kids.  Oil heat forced air. This a great home for a young family starting home or a couple looking to downsize to single level living.  Now at highest and best for Monday the 8th at 5pm .
data.whatILove: Brand new above ground pool, chicken coup inside shed with electricity.
